ygData.msgSnippet: Well, there is the Lair of the Splitpaw Gnolls, commonly known as Paw.  It is in S. Karana and is for levels 5 to 18 or so.  Solusek s Eye is a NASTY place
ygData.messageBody:
Well, there is the Lair of the Splitpaw Gnolls, commonly known as Paw. It
is in S. Karana and is for levels 5 to 18 or so. Solusek's Eye is a NASTY
place (probably one of the hardest places in Norrath now) since it has lava
traps AND when I walked in the door at level 20, I saw a PET of a Greater
Kobold Shaman that con'd Red to me, so I assumed the master was DEEP red and
immediately left.

Djar Lightbringer(Tarew Marr Server)
Servant of Light, Deliverer of the Truth to Norrath



-----Original Message-----
